{"tid":2392054,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國安1月29日拘捕 2 男 1 女，罪名 資助他人分裂國家 及 洗黑錢，與傑斯案件有關","createTime":"2021-02-02T14:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T15:31:10.000Z","uid":219007,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bca26947186334d7ca2a981a454bfb7f2adbaaf5","tid":2392054,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:39:48.000Z","msg":"【警以國安法拘三人 首次沒即時公佈】<br />\n<br />\n警務處處長鄧炳強今日（2 日）表示，《港區國安法》實施以來，警方拘捕 97 人，當中 8 人已被檢控。翻查資料，截至上月中，被指違國安法被捕的只有 94 人。<br />\n<br />\n其後被捕的另外 3 人，究竟何時被捕、被捕原因、案情，警方從未主動交代。直到今日傍晚，《立場》向警方查詢的四小時後，警方才發稿，交代警方國安處在 1 月 29 日以「以金錢或者其他財物資助他人分裂國家」及洗黑錢罪名拘捕 2 男 1 女，年齡介乎 28 歲至 58 歲，與去年 11 月 D100 網台主持傑斯等人被捕案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3865157366903188/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fphotos%2Fa.720050934747196%2F3865157366903188%2F&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=93d2df06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/photos/a.720050934747196/3865157366903188/</a>"},{"pid":"9d7e55329cc99e88ed79414e744053358db378ef","tid":2392054,"uid":290118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:40:42.000Z","msg":"開始鬼鬼祟祟拉人"},{"pid":"ee4347257b17d4b5f815a2aeb49516df599b96e0","tid":2392054,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9d7e55329cc99e88ed79414e744053358db378ef","tid":2392054,"uid":290118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:40:42.000Z","msg":"開始鬼鬼祟祟拉人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:42:04.000Z","msg":"常態化"},{"pid":"202e3b95a4cc09318b86f7c0c692fba35ea4cd75","tid":2392054,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T14:43:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbcca2070402856b9f793960fdda5233be913b8","tid":2392054,"uid":251732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"ci